If the electoral system can't be fixed, it must be overhauled. That’s the view of One South Africa Movement's Mmusi Maimane. He says the amendment bill, as it stands, will always favour political parties.#DStv403 JOHANNESBURG - If the electoral system can't be fixed, it must be overhauled according to One South Africa Movement's Mmusi Maimane. READ: Parliament should be overhauled: analyst He says the amendment bill, as it stands, will always favour political parties. He says the system can be proportional or fair, but it can't be both.